@startuml architecture
!theme aws-orange

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam defaultFontColor #000000
skinparam componentFontColor #000000
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam ArrowThickness 0.8
skinparam LineThickness 0.8
skinparam ranksep 24
skinparam nodesep 18
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam DefaultTextAlignment left

skinparam componentBackgroundColor<<core>> #FFF3CD
skinparam componentBorderColor<<core>>     #C88719
skinparam componentBackgroundColor<<algo>> #E3F2FD
skinparam componentBorderColor<<algo>>     #1565C0
skinparam componentBackgroundColor<<util>> #F2F2F2
skinparam componentBorderColor<<util>>     #616161

top to bottom direction
title Architecture Freeze Artifact Lifecycle

component "==<size:14><b>Project Manager</b></size>\nproblem statement\nfreeze request" <<core>> as PM
component "==<size:14><b>Architecture Expert</b></size>\nboundary / NFR freeze\nblueprint selection" <<core>> as Arch
component "==<size:14><b>architecture_freeze</b></size>\ncontract_freeze artifact\nrepo-local refs only" <<util>> as Freeze
component "==<size:14><b>Blueprint Pair</b></size>\n.puml source\n.md lifecycle metadata" <<util>> as Blueprint
component "==<size:14><b>Downstream Roles</b></size>\ncoding / testing / traceability" <<algo>> as Downstream

PM --> Arch
Arch --> Freeze
Freeze --> Blueprint
Freeze --> Downstream

note right of Freeze
handoff keeps a reference to architecture_freeze;
it does not duplicate the full freeze content
end note
@enduml
